WEBVTT

00:00.253 --> 00:03.039
- <i>Previously on</i> Underground...
- I made a plan.

00:03.073 --> 00:05.179
<i>Going back to get Momma and James.</i>

00:05.219 --> 00:07.561
But ain't nothin' ever go as planned.

00:07.689 --> 00:09.425
You can still bite, can't you?

00:09.458 --> 00:12.459
Everywhere you take me,
there's no reflections of us.

00:12.506 --> 00:14.875
<i>It's just rich and white.</i>

00:14.908 --> 00:17.578
- How can we get to the Black Rose?
- You got to go through her momma.

00:17.611 --> 00:19.213
<i>She the only thing that girl care about.</i>

00:19.245 --> 00:20.646
It work!

00:20.680 --> 00:21.914
<i>Ain't gonna be long</i>

00:21.948 --> 00:23.317
<i>'fore he do whatever I want.</i>

00:23.349 --> 00:24.851
<i>Good.</i>

00:24.884 --> 00:27.854
'Cause you gonna use him
to get me off this island.

00:35.529 --> 00:37.331
That one right there.

00:37.364 --> 00:38.724
"Mahk."

00:38.758 --> 00:39.885
"Make."

00:41.020 --> 00:43.169
You said "A"s sound like "ah."

00:43.203 --> 00:45.172
It does until it doesn't.

00:45.205 --> 00:46.907
You see that "E" on the end there?

00:46.940 --> 00:48.574
Changes it.

00:49.125 --> 00:51.452
Why they ain't put it
at the beginning, then?

00:52.145 --> 00:54.047
Daddy, someone's coming.

00:58.475 --> 01:00.978
- They got us trapped!
- Hide the papers.

01:02.011 --> 01:03.180
You run as fast as you can.

01:03.213 --> 01:05.182
Go! Don't look back.

01:07.000 --> 01:13.074
